<script type="text/javascript">
(function($) {
 
    AJS.$("#customfield_11100 option[value='-1']").remove(); //Removes the default value "None"
    function convertMulti(id){
        if (AJS.$('#'+id+"-textarea").length == 0){
            new AJS.MultiSelect({
                element: $("#"+id),
                itemAttrDisplayed: "label",
                errorMessage: AJS.params.multiselectComponentsError
            });
        }
    }
  
    AJS.toInit(function(){   
        convertMulti("customfield_11100");
    });
    JIRA.bind(JIRA.Events.NEW_CONTENT_ADDED, function (e, context) {
        AJS.$("#customfield_11100 option[value='-1']").remove();
        convertMulti("customfield_11100");
    });
  
})(AJS.$);
</script>
